  Changing the properties of a CoordinateTransform attached to a patch leads to
  wrong bounding boxes.
  
2009-06-07 Saalfeld
  MovingLeastSquaresTransform.setMatches() can throw two exceptions.  TrakEM2
  catches all Exceptions silently at many places.  Inspect all these places for
  sideeffects.
